data.description: Prepare to be impressed. Welcome to this freshly upgraded 4 bedroom/4 bathroom/2 car garage home (with the ability to easily wall off the upstairs loft into a 5th bedroom – allowing for 4 bedrooms on the upper level!) Welcome to  set on 1.11 ACRES with unobstructed PIKES PEAK VIEWS –a rarity in todays market. Walking inside you might start humming "isn't she lovely" by Stevie Wonder as this home looks straight out of a Pinterest page. The front sitting room features large windows and ample natural light. Newly refinished hardwood floors flow throughout the main level. The kitchen features white cabinets, butcher block counters, a deep farm house sink, modern hardware and stainless steel appliances. Double doors off the kitchen lead to the expansive outdoor deck and patio. Artfully designed, imagine sitting with your loved ones and watching the entire front range light up at sunset over Pikes Peak. Back inside, the main level is finished off with the family room (with a cozy gas fireplace) half bathroom and laundry room. Moving upstairs a HUGE master is waiting to wow you. The master bedroom is open to the upstairs loft making it the perfect place for a home office, baby room, sitting area or easily wall it off to make a 5th bedroom. The primary bedroom is complete with an en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet. The upper level features two additional bedrooms in addition to the master and a full bath. The equally impressive basement is the perfect place to relax and hangout with friends or provide a private space for your guests. The basement features a large family room (with a second gas fireplace) one bedroom and one full bathroom. Don't forget the updated wet bar which features epoxy counters giving is a sleek and polished look! You don't want to miss out on this special home that has so much to offer. Love where you live and make it yours today!
